# Legacy: el botón ✨ "Generate commit message" de Source Control NO lee
# .cursor/rules/, pero sí puede leer este archivo en la raíz del repo.

When auto-generating a Git commit message for this repository:

- Use Conventional Commits: `type(scope): subject`
- types: feat, fix, docs, chore, refactor, test, ci, build, perf
- subject: imperative, no trailing period, max 72 characters
- body: optional, each line max 100 characters (use multiple short lines)
- never write one long paragraph in the body
- do not add Co-authored-by or other trailers
- write in English
